  			<h1 data-element="title" class="title Heading4"></h1>
        		  				<p id="awesomeFBLikeButton"></p>
          	  			<p data-element="content" class="content">Though casual chic may sound like an oxymoron, the truth is that you can look chic in almost anything you wear (sans workout gear and pajamas). The key to mastering the art of casual chic is to combine comfortable clothing with a hint of sophisticated flair. That flair may be demonstrated by your shoe choice, accessories, hair or even absolute confidence in your appearance. Once you've mastered the casual chic look, you'll always have something to wear no matter where you go, be it a cocktail party, grocery store or barbecue.</p>
  			<small data-element="credit" class="credit">Getty Images</small>
